entry.title: Behind Hamas's Piecemeal Hostage Strategy
entry.content: The militant group has freed four hostages but is seeking to extract more concessions from the Israelis for the release of others.

entry.title: Armenia Seeks Western Support as Relations With Russia Deteriorate
entry.content: As fears of another war grow, Armenia purchases French air defenses and says Russia failed to abide by its obligations as an ally.
